snippet.title: Othercide | GDC Gameplay Trailer 2019
snippet.description: Othercide, an upcoming turn-based strategy game, revealed itself in a new trailer at GDC 2019. Enter a brutal world under assault from terrifying creatures and endure brutal conditions in a visually stunning world. Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/798490/Othercide/
